<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero-small">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="accordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                What is the CareerPath psychometric test?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                The CareerPath assessment is a 50-question test divided into five sections: Aptitude, Personality Traits, Career Interests, Emotional Intelligence, and Skills &amp; Abilities. It is designed for students from 10th standard to graduation level.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                How long does the assessment take?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Most students complete the full assessment in 30 to 45 minutes. You can navigate between sections using the progress controls, and your answers are saved as you go.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                Is the assessment free?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Yes. CareerPath offers free psychometric assessments and career report generation for eligible students in our target communities. Counselor guidance sessions are also provided at no cost during the pilot phase.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                How is my counselor assigned?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                After you submit your test, the system generates a rule-based career report and matches you with a counselor whose specialization aligns with your recommended career path. If multiple counselors match, one is selected randomly to balance workload.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                How do I connect with my counselor?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Once assigned, your counselor's name, specialization, email, and phone number appear on your dashboard and career report. Contact them directly via email or phone for offline guidance sessions.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                Can I become a counselor on this platform?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Yes. Select "I am a Career Counselor" during registration and provide your area of specialization and years of experience. Once registered, you can view assigned students and manage session status from your counselor dashboard.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button type="button" class="accordion-header">
                Is my data secure?
                <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-body">
                CareerPath follows strict data protection practices. Your assessment responses and personal information are stored securely and shared only with your assigned counselor. Read our Privacy Policy for full details.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
